contentrichtext.text: '''Rockman''' can refer to: * The Japanese name of the [[video game]] character [[Mega Man (character)|Mega Man]], as well as the [[Mega_Man_(video game)|first game]] in the [[Mega_Man_(franchise)|franchise]] * [[Alexis Rockman]], an American contemporary artist known for his paintings depicting the precarious relationship between man and nature * [[David Rockman]], (Fearless Dave) founder of the [[Dharma Temple of the Magic Fish Head]], a sect of [[Discordianism]] based on Rock and Roll Music. * [[Rockman (amplifier)]], a brand name of headphone guitar amplifiers and other music technology products * Rockman Rock, a pseudonym of [[Jimmy Cauty]] from electronic music group The KLF * [[Rockman (comics)]], an early [[Marvel Comics]] hero * [[Rock Men]], characters in the Conker series * [[Rockman (website)]], a Norwegian music-website {{disambig}}
